performance_details.query: q = load "lead1"; q = filter q by {{cell(time_dropdown.selection, 0, "current").asDateRange("date('CreatedDate_Year', 'CreatedDate_Month', 'CreatedDate_Day')")}}; q = group q by 'Id'; q = foreach q generate first('Name') as 'Name', first('Company') as 'Company', first('Country') as 'Country',  first('UserOrQueueName') as 'UserOrQueueName', first('Rating') as 'Rating', first('LeadSource') as 'LeadSource', first('IsConverted') as 'Converted', first('ConvertedDate') as 'ConvertedDate', sum('LeadAge') as 'Age';

conversion_rate.query: leads = load "lead1"; leads = filter leads by {{cell(time_dropdown.selection, 0, "current").asDateRange("date('CreatedDate_Year', 'CreatedDate_Month', 'CreatedDate_Day')")}}; converted = filter leads by 'IsConverted' == "true"; converted = group converted by all; converted = foreach converted generate count() as 'count_converted'; leads = group leads by all; leads = foreach leads generate count() as 'count_all'; q = group leads by all full, converted by all; q = foreach q generate sum(leads['count_all']) as 'count_all', sum(converted['count_converted']) as 'count_converted'; q = foreach q generate coalesce('count_converted' / 'count_all', 0) as 'sum_percent';
